name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: LeadLabs: Personality AI for Humanizing Outreach

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Build warm relationships with generative AI by understanding personality and personalizing communication accordingly.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
LeadLabs is an AI tool that helps sales reps reduce hours of prospect research to seconds. It helps write emails and messages in a click by analyzing the prospect's personality, persona, tonality, content, personal attributes & more. 

Build warm relationships with prospects with the all-in-one warm outreach tool.

Additionally, stand out in crowded inboxes with interactive GIFs and story-based microsites. Recording and pasting a GIF in the email editor has never been easier.

Let go of using the same vanilla framework for each prospect in your list and start tailoring emails and messages for each prospect based on relevant signals combined with personality and boost reply rates.

*****What's new in 2.5.5?*****
- Our most advanced 2.0 writing model is now live
- Analyze profiles with one button instead of two
- New signals in account analysis
- New editor makes it's debut in content generator
- Shortcuts in the writing editor
- Fixed minor UI issues
- Fixed comment generator issue and self authored content issue
- Squished those pesky bugs
